=> Fix: Update CyodaRepository to implement the correct CrudRepository interface methods exactly (method names, parameters and return types), define any expected constants (FORMAT), and ensure the httpUtils methods used match the expected return types. The safest solution is to open the CrudRepository interface, copy the exact method signatures, and implement them.

